## مكوّنات التنفيذ داخل `aix-format`

### 1. Schema (schemas/)
أضف:
- `schemas/unified-bom.schema.json` — JSON Schema للـ unified_bom extension
- `schemas/saas-ref.schema.json` — تعريف كائن SaaS reference
- `schemas/ai-ref.schema.json` — تعريف كائن AI/model reference

### 2. Core (core/)
أضف:
- `core/unified-bom/collector.ts` — يقرأ AIX manifests ويبني BOM graph
- `core/unified-bom/correlator.ts` — يربط SaaS + AI + Infra refs
- `core/unified-bom/risk-engine.ts` — يحسب risk score ويولّد findings
- `core/unified-bom/exporter.ts` — يصدّر compliance bundles

### 3. CI (github actions)
أضف Job جديد بعد `aix-validation`:

```yaml
- name: Generate Unified BOM
  run: node scripts/generate-unified-bom.mjs
  
- name: Sign BOM (SLSA provenance)
  uses: sigstore/cosign-action@v3
  with:
    args: sign-blob ./dist/unified-bom.json
    
- name: Upload BOM artifact
  uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
  with:
    name: unified-bom
    path: ./dist/unified-bom.json
```

### 4. MCP Server (packages/mcp-server أو ما يعادله)
أضف tools:

```typescript
// list_unified_bom
{
  name: "list_unified_bom",
  description: "Returns the full Unified BOM for a given AIX agent ID",
  inputSchema: { agent_id: string }
}

// export_compliance_bundle
{
  name: "export_compliance_bundle",
  description: "Exports a compliance-ready artifact bundle",
  inputSchema: { agent_id: string, framework: "EU_AI_ACT" | "CISA" | "NIST" }
}

// trace_data_lineage
{
  name: "trace_data_lineage",
  description: "Traces all datasets linked to an agent and their provenance",
  inputSchema: { agent_id: string }
}

// explain_risk_posture
{
  name: "explain_risk_posture",
  description: "Returns risk summary and open gaps for a given agent",
  inputSchema: { agent_id: string }
}
```

